TITLE: Update Status Footer
DESCRIPTION: Updates the visual status indicators (dot and text) in the UI based on the provided status type, text, and optional details. It manages the CSS classes for the status dot to reflect the current state.

SOURCE: https://github.com/davila7/claude-code-templates/blob/main/cli-tool/src/analytics-web/chats_mobile.html#_snippet_45

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
updateStatus(status, text, details = '') {
  const statusDot = document.getElementById('statusDot');
  const statusText = document.getElementById('statusText');
  const statusDetails = document.getElementById('statusDetails');
  if (!statusDot || !statusText || !statusDetails) return;

  statusDot.className = 'status-dot';
  statusDot.classList.add(status);

  statusText.textContent = text;
  statusDetails.textContent = details;
}
```

